Nigerian music star,  David Adeleke, popularly known as “Davido” has taken to his social media handles to celebrate his fiancee, Chioma, who is a year older. The ‘assurance’ crooner via his Twitter handle on Thursday shared lovely photos of him and fiancee,  describing her as a strong woman. He wrote: “HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO THE STRONGEST WOMAN I KNOW !!!  !!!!  !!!” The music star and father of three however lamented the ongoing lockdown will hinder him from celebrating her the way he wishes to. “Ohhhh Man if we wasn’t on lockdown u already know we for turn the city upside down!! !!!! My dear wife, may your birthday be as happy as you have made me. AND THATS ON GANG!…. ”  